Text: Fw Directions to John and CathysHello Here are the directions to our house Directions from I and Beltway going towards Sugarland When youpass Interstate this means that your exit is coming up Your exit is GenoaRed Bluff Rd It is marked as the last free exit Exit GenoaRed Bluff Rd and take a right at the light Proceed miles on winding road to the first stoplight Red Bluff and take a right Go about miles and the road basically ends at Highway Take a right on Highway Take a right at the first light Repsdorph Take a left at the first street Acadiana into Lake Cove Harbor Takethe firstright onto Vermillion Street Take a left at the next street Lakeside At the third stop sign take a left onto Du Lac Trace We are the second house on the left See you soon Cathy
